name: Han
review: 'Super cute van with everything that we needed for a prefect getaway from the city.'

name: Meg
review: 'Such a cool van! Beautifully revamped with cute features and a comfy bed. We took the van to Lillooet lake and had the best views. Can't wait for another adventure with Brandi!'

name: Steve
review: 'We loved our trip in Brandi! We were able to camp in places that aren't possible with a tent. I will definitely be renting it again!'
